From 2275f5994de085be0cd7d3d78f2c8e6553d7e555 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Fri, 24 Apr 2026 00:17:45 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: SSE error streams + LiveLog always shows + diagnostics
 button
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- API verify route: outer catch now returns SSE stream instead of JSON 500,
  so the frontend LiveLog console can display server errors properly
- Frontend: add initial log entries before fetch so LiveLog shows immediately
- Frontend: always show LiveLog in error state (not conditionally)
- Frontend: add 'Diagnóstico del servidor' button that calls /api/debug
- Frontend: show debug info panel with copy-to-clipboard
- db.ts: safe initialization with try/catch fallback
